{"tid":677224,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"越渴望勝利雲加發現，中間隔著百萬元；我想見的不敗 只有懷念，不懂 怎去再贏波","createTime":"2018-05-25T04:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T17:19:30.000Z","uid":36497,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0538d17a4e1ae78a0d30fcfd7f94008bfa81af8a","tid":677224,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"愛美麗 無可避免 倫敦總依戀雲加<br />\n乘早機 忍耐著呵欠 完全為見你一面<br />\n<br />\n尋不到 塵封不敗 回不到零四那天<br />\n靈氣大概早被污染 誰為了生活不變<br />\n<br />\n越渴望勝利雲加發現<br />\n中間隔著百萬元<br />\n我想見的不敗 只有懷念<br />\n不懂 怎去再贏波<br />\n<br />\n像雲加往日還會抽煙<br />\n不知你怎麼變遷<br />\n似等了一百年 忽爾明白<br />\n即使再教阿 成熟地表演 不如不教<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa18b51bf6a4b5c60ce1071bbaf3ffe1596a4843","tid":677224,"uid":64699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d384d448a0374f6fa9eaa3ce2512d7fc8b86803c","tid":677224,"uid":137238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14e0816c83322ee0e63d8c0539c25fb5c8327af","tid":677224,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa18b51bf6a4b5c60ce1071bbaf3ffe1596a4843","tid":677224,"uid":64699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89919603f8b99ec1a951053c1235568091706a2","tid":677224,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d384d448a0374f6fa9eaa3ce2512d7fc8b86803c","tid":677224,"uid":137238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04